## 11. INCUBATORS & ACCELERATORS (Comprehensive)

---

### 11.1 IIT Bombay -- SINE (Society for Innovation and Entrepreneurship)

- **What:** India's first incubator-linked VC fund (Y-Point Venture Capital Fund, INR 250 Cr target corpus). 20+ years of startup support.
- **Offers:** Incubation space, mentorship, seed funding, access to Y-Point VC Fund. Focus: AI, healthcare, deep-tech, clean-tech, life sciences.
- **Equity:** Typically 2-5% equity stake.
- **Eligibility:** Tech startups, preference for IIT Bombay-connected but open to external.
- **Fit for Samay Sarthi:** STRONG -- healthcare and AI are explicit focus sectors. INR 250 Cr VC fund provides direct investment pipeline.
- **URL:** https://www.sineiitb.org/

---

### 11.2 IIT Madras Incubation Cell (IITMIC)

- **What:** India's largest deep-tech startup hub. 500+ startups incubated with combined valuation exceeding INR 53,000 Crore. 11,000+ direct jobs created.
- **Offers:** Incubation, mentorship, funding access, Nirmaan pre-incubation program, connections to 100+ new deep-tech startups annually.
- **Equity:** Small equity stake.
- **Eligibility:** Students, faculty, alumni, and external entrepreneurs.
- **Fit for Samay Sarthi:** STRONG -- AI/healthcare intersection is strong at IIT-M. Deep-tech focus aligns well.
- **URL:** https://www.iitm.ac.in/research-park/incubation-cell and http://rtbi.in/incubationiitm/

---

### 11.3 IIT Delhi -- FITT (Foundation for Innovation and Technology Transfer)

- **What:** Industry-academia interface for research translation, technology development, IPR management, startup incubation.
- **Offers:** Incubation, mentorship, access to Microsoft UNNATI AI Accelerator (healthcare-focused), FITT's corporate incubation programs.
- **Eligibility:** Tech startups.
- **Recent:** Microsoft + FITT launched UNNATI AI Accelerator specifically for healthcare, education, agriculture, sustainability startups in Tier-II/III.
- **Fit for Samay Sarthi:** STRONG -- UNNATI AI Accelerator directly targets healthcare AI startups. FITT's defense connections (DefConnect 4.0) could enable defense-health crossover.
- **URL:** https://fitt-iitd.in/

---

### 11.4 IIT Kanpur -- SIIC (Startup Incubation and Innovation Centre)

- **What:** Equity-based incubation program (18 months). Includes BIRAC-supported bio-incubator for healthcare and agriculture.
- **Offers:** Customized incubation, mentorship, bio-incubator with lab facilities, NIRMAN Accelerator Programme.
- **Eligibility:** Tech startups with venture-backable potential.
- **Fit for Samay Sarthi:** MODERATE -- bio-incubator focus is more wet-lab oriented, but the general incubation program fits.
- **URL:** http://www.siicincubator.com/

---

### 11.5 IIT Gandhinagar -- IIEC

- **What:** Innovation and Entrepreneurship Center at IIT Gandhinagar.
- **Offers:** Wet and dry labs, rapid prototyping infrastructure (hardware + software), incubation for high-tech startups.
- **Eligibility:** Alumni and external startups.
- **URL:** https://iieciitgn.com/

