  - **Pfizer INDovation:** Up to INR 60 Lakh grants for MedTech startups (see section 11.12)
  - **Techtonic:** Deep-tech accelerator
- **Eligibility:** Science and technology startups addressing social, economic, environmental challenges.
- **Fit for Samay Sarthi:** STRONG -- Quest for Healthcare and the Tata Trusts-PATH Impact Lab are directly relevant.
- **URL:** https://www.socialalpha.org/

