### 11.10 AIIMS Delhi -- CMIE (Centre for Medical Innovation & Entrepreneurship)

- **What:** BIRAC-BioNEST bio-incubator at AIIMS Delhi. 60th Bio-Incubator under the scheme. Facilities at NCI Jhajjar campus (13,000 sqft) and AIIMS Ansari Nagar (3,000 sqft).
- **Offers:** Incubation space, clinical mentorship from AIIMS faculty, proximity to India's top medical institution, access to patient data for validation.
- **Focus Areas:** Precision/molecular medicine, AI-enabled medical devices, imaging, data science in medicine, digital health.
- **Eligibility:** Healthcare/medtech startups.
- **Fit for Samay Sarthi:** EXCELLENT -- being incubated at AIIMS provides unparalleled clinical credibility. Already have AIIMS Jodhpur validation; AIIMS Delhi incubation would be the next level. "AI-enabled" and "digital health" are explicitly listed.
- **URL:** https://cmie-aiims.in/
- **Action:** HIGH PRIORITY -- apply for incubation.

